Title: Stop showing longer time ranges in size_trend
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1729235563
Edition: cre
Level: 1
Version: 2.2.0p36

In case you're trend calculation (using <code>size_trend</code>) has a very small growth rate, your check may have displayed a very high "Time left until full".

We now stop showing the message if the time until your resource is full is more than 10 years.
